    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The placement are really good in our college. In last year the placements of the our mechanical engineering department is 90 to 95 persent and average package is 3LPA",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "I like placement of electrical department latest passout batch get 100%placement from electrical engineering department also I like teachers behaviour , performance, collaboration, and motivate to students for their future jobs or future career and .",
          "name": "Disha Santosh Gunjal",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Our collage is so clean n neat.Each n every corner is so fresh.many people's are hire to maintain the collage clean.our principle very strict about cleanllyness.",
          "name": "Sakshi",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Campus of our collage is so beautiful and green.teir is minimum one ecours area of garden name as amphitheatre.and the big trees is such a lovely.flower plants and so on.",
          "name": "Sakshi",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Networking:  The college had a strong alumni network, which was a great resource for internships, mentorships, and job placements. Industry tie-ups ensured regular workshops, seminars, and company visits.",
          "name": "Tambe kaveri Sukhdev",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Cultural and Social Opportunities:  Numerous clubs and societies catered to diverse interests, including drama, robotics, sports, and social causes. This helped in developing interpersonal and leadership skills. Cultural festivals and inter-college c",
          "name": "Tambe kaveri Sukhdev",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Academic Growth:  The curriculum was well-structured, offering both theoretical knowledge and practical exposure. Professors were approachable, especially during office hours, which helped in clearing doubts.",
          "name": "Tambe kaveri Sukhdev",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Hostels are near to the college which makes girls security",
          "name": "Pawar Poonam Ganpat",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Classes are well maintain and cleanliness in the campus",
          "name": "Pawar Poonam Ganpat",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "I like the college campus there is greenery very much",
          "name": "Pawar Poonam Ganpat",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The fee of the college is more. And there are many fees that we have to pay in semester like a fees of exam fee. Industrial visit fee etc.",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "I don't like ladies common room. it is very compactn small",
          "name": "Sakshi",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Collage drinking water is smelly n taestless n harmful",
          "name": "Sakshi",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Our collage road is very rough. In monsoon their is many problems",
          "name": "Sakshi",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Extracurriculars were encouraged, but academic workload often made it difficult for students to balance their passions with studies.",
          "name": "Tambe kaveri Sukhdev",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Rigid Curriculum:  Some courses lacked flexibility in terms of electives, making it hard to explore interests outside one’s major.",
          "name": "Tambe kaveri Sukhdev",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Limited Mental Health Support:  While the academic environment was competitive, there were insufficient mental health resources like counselors or stress management programs. Stigma around mental health made it hard for students to seek help openly.",
          "name": "Tambe kaveri Sukhdev",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "There is lack of discipline in the campus",
          "name": "Pawar Poonam Ganpat",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Teachers are not very cooperative towards student",
          "name": "Pawar Poonam Ganpat",
